The last scene I saw was the two of them with sad

It feels like we're finally reaching the climax.
It's been tough up to this point, but I feel like
we'll be okay as long as it's with Aeru.

Lira, who is next to me, says such things, but
I've made it this far not only by my own strength,
but also thanks to the support of my other
companions.

Well, I don't have to be so modest. I've made it
this far because Aeru was here. I agree with Lira
on this.

That's right! Look, even Light is saying the same
thing.
I'm not joking, thank you as always, Aeru.

Lira's face looks unusually serious as she says
this, so I gaze at her intently.

...I think she's beautiful. I hadn't been
conscious of it because she was always so close.

The series of events surrounding the curse may
have brought about some kind of change in our
relationship.

Suddenly, white light envelops the surroundings,
and Lira's voice is heard right next to me. I
hurriedly reach out my hand.

I might have been touched just like that, and my
consciousness melted away into the light.
Are you ready in your heart?
あ、いえ、まだちょっと・・・
